'''[[西藏|西藏]]的[[人权|人权]]'''是一个有争议的话题。据中国大陆境外部分媒体报道，西藏侵犯人权的行为包括限制[[宗教自由|宗教]]、信仰和结社自由；{{link-en|任意逮捕和拘留|Arbitrary arrest and detention|任意逮捕}}；{{link-en|虐待囚犯|Prisoner abuse|拘留期间的虐待}}，包括[[酷刑|酷刑]]；{{link-en|强迫堕胎|Forced abortion}}和[[强制绝育|绝育]]。宗教方面的人权问题，主要与宗教和政治人物有关，例如[[第十四世达赖喇嘛|第十四世达赖喇嘛]]的流亡，是经常受到批评的话题，另外[[第十一世班禅争议|第十一世班禅]]和[[第十七世噶瑪巴爭議|第十七世噶瑪巴]]的認定方面也有著重大爭議。

根据历史文献等资料，1951年以前，西藏由神权政体<ref>Samten G. Karmay, [http://www.tibetwrites.org/?Religion-and-Politics-commentary Religion and Politics: commentary] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tibetwrites.org/?Religion-and-Politics-commentary |date=20160305233421 }} {{Cite web |url=http://www.tibetwrites.org/?religion-and-politics-commentary |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305233421/http://www.tibetwrites.org/?religion-and-politics-commentary |dead-url=unfit }}, September 2008: "from 1642 the Ganden Potrang, the official seat of the government in Drepung Monastery, came to symbolize the supreme power in both the theory and practice of a theocratic government. This was indeed a political triumph that Buddhism had never known in its history in Tibet."</ref>或[[西藏农奴制度|农奴制]]统治，社会等级制度类似种姓制度<ref>{{cite book|last=Fjeld|first=Heidi|title=Commoners and Nobles:Hereditary Divisions in Tibet|publisher=Nordic Institute of Asian Studies|year=2003|page=5|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=g0V5lV_M-SYC|isbn=9788791114175|access-date=2015-11-15|archive-date=2020-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200823230735/https://books.google.com/books?id=g0V5lV_M-SYC|dead-url=no}}</ref>；然而過去可能的人權問題，不代表現在可能的人權問題不該被重視；对于中共政權入主西藏後的西藏人權實際狀況，多方存在着爭議，西藏人權問題也是[[中華人民共和國人權|中華人民共和國人權]]最主要的焦點之一。

==部分國際看法==
根据1992年[[国际特赦组织|国际特赦组织]]的一份报告（未经核实的数字），中国的司法标准，包括[[西藏自治区|西藏自治区]]的司法标准，没有达到“国际标准”。报告指控[[中国共产党|中国共产党]]<ref name="aiamnesty">Amnesty International, [http://www.tibetjustice.org/materials/un/un8annex2.1.html Amnesty International: "China - Amnesty International's concerns in Tibet"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090912004834/http://www.tibetjustice.org/materials/un/un8annex2.1.html |date=2009-09-12 }}, Secretary-General's Report: Situation in Tibet, E/CN.4/1992/37</ref>政府关押[[政治犯|政治犯]]和[[良心犯|良心犯]]；虐待被拘留者，包括酷刑，以及面对虐待不作为；使用死刑；{{link-en|法外处决|Extrajudicial killing}}<ref name="aiamnesty" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hrweb.org/ai/aidoc.html |title=Amnesty International Documents |publisher=Hrweb.org |access-date=2012-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315090003/http://www.hrweb.org/ai/aidoc.html |archive-date=2012-03-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；以及强迫堕胎和绝育<ref name="Goldstein 1991 285–303" /><ref name="crin.org">{{cite web |title=Genocide in Tibet - Children of Despair |website=Child Rights International Network |publisher=Campaign Free Tibet |url=http://www.crin.org/docs/resources/treaties/crc.12/China_CFT2_NGO_Report.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119081639/http://www.crin.org/docs/resources/treaties/crc.12/China_CFT2_NGO_Report.pdf |archive-date=2012-01-19 |quote=There is a great deal of evidence and detailed testimony, which indicates that [forced abortion and sterilisation] has been Chinese policy in Tibet for many years |access-date=2021-02-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。20世纪80年代末发表的一系列报告证实了这一说法，即中国正在迫使藏人坚持严格的计划生育，包括强迫堕胎、绝育，甚至[[杀婴|杀婴]]。<ref name="Goldstein 1991 285–303">{{Cite journal|title=China's Birth Control Policy in the Tibet Autonomous Region|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_asian-survey_1991-03_31_3/page/285|journal=[[Asian_Survey|Asian Survey]]|author-link=Melvyn Goldstein|first1=Melvyn|last1=Goldstein|first2=Beall|last2=Cynthia|date=March 1991|volume=31|issue=3|pages=285–303|jstor=2645246|doi=10.1525/as.1991.31.3.00p0043x}}</ref>[[路透社|路透社]]2020年的一份报告指出，西藏人口的15％是人权组织认为具有[[强迫劳动|强制性]]的大规模劳工计划的一部分。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Cadell|first=Cate|date=2020-09-22|title=China sharply expands mass labor program in Tibet|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-rights-tibet-exclusive/exclusive-china-sharply-expands-mass-labor-program-in-tibet-idUSKCN26D0GT|access-date=2020-09-24|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426123917/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-rights-tibet-exclusive/exclusive-china-sharply-expands-mass-labor-program-in-tibet-idUSKCN26D0GT|dead-url=no}}</ref>批评中共的人士说，中共旨在消除“分裂主义、[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]和宗教极端主义三大邪恶”的官方目标被用作侵犯人权的借口。<ref>Simon Denyer, [https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/dec/08/china-party-dissent-xinjiang-tibet China cracks down on aggrieved party cadres in Xinjiang and Tibet] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229201516/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/dec/08/china-party-dissent-xinjiang-tibet |date=2016-12-29 }}, The Guardian, 8 December 2015.</ref>

部分媒体与国家声称由于中国没有[[中華人民共和國媒體|新闻自由]]<ref name="news.bbc.co.uk">{{Cite news|date=2019-04-26|title=Tibet profile|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-pacific-16689779|access-date=2020-11-20|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027205044/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-pacific-16689779|dead-url=no}}</ref>，西藏的媒体受到中国领导层的严格控制，因此很难明确界定侵犯人权的范围。<ref name="statedept09">US State Department, Bureau of Democracy, Human Rights, and Labor, ''[https://web.archive.org/web/20090226175344/http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2008/eap/119037.htm#tibet 2008 Human Rights Report: China (includes Tibet, Hong Kong, and Macau)]'', February 25, 2009</ref>

==中华人民共和国官方==
中华人民共和国官方聲稱，与西方的报道和批评相反，中国官方统计数据显示，西藏的人权状况有了巨大改善。西藏是过去几十年中国所有[[中华人民共和国行政区划|省级地区]]中人口增长最快的地区之一。截至2018年，西藏自治区人口达到343万人，比1952年增长198%。根据2010年第六次全国人口普查，西藏自治区常住人口300.22万人，有50个民族，其中藏族人口271.64万人，占90.48%；汉族人口24.53万人，占8.17%；其他少数民族人口4.05万人，占1.35%。<ref name="Tibet.cn">{{Cite news|date=2020-07-17|title=中国社科院专家：60余年西藏人口增长近两倍 藏族人口占90%以上|language=zh-CN|url=http://www.tibet.cn/cn/rediscovery/202007/t20200717_6820418.html|access-date=2020-12-10|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109162719/http://www.tibet.cn/cn/rediscovery/202007/t20200717_6820418.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>西藏的人均预期寿命达到70.6岁，比上世纪50年代初西藏[[西藏和平解放|并入]]中华人民共和国时的35.5岁有所提高。<ref name="People.cn">{{Cite news|date=2019-05-24|title=西藏人均预期寿命超过70岁 提前完成2020年预期目标|language=zh-CN|url=http://xz.people.com.cn/n2/2019/0524/c138901-32975320.html|access-date=2020-12-10}}</ref>

